HEADWORD: Disposer
<hw>Dis*pos"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, disposes; a regulator; a director; a bestower.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Absolute lord and <qex>disposer</qex> of all things.</q>
<rj><qau>Barrow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disposingly</ent>⟦br⟧
